  "title": "NEW! Business Analyst (Junior) - Contract",
  "description": "<p>Job Duties:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support project delivery and implementation, ensuring quality and timely completion.</li>\n  <li>Gather and document business requirements, rules, and solutions aligned with project objectives.</li>\n  <li>Work with stakeholders and project leads to maintain timelines and resolve issues proactively.</li>\n  <li>Develop and execute UAT, including test scenarios, documentation, and defect tracking with IT.</li>\n  <li>Lead discussions on defect resolution and follow up on system fixes.</li>\n  <li>Prepare training materials, conduct user training, and perform post-deployment verification.</li>\n  <li>Drive continuous improvement by identifying opportunities to enhance processes and system efficiency.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1 year experience in insurance industry</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills</li>\n  <li>Good verbal and written communication skills and good interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Word format and attention it to Rachel Yeo (R22104385).</p>\n<p>Shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>\n<p>Data provided is for recruitment purposes only</p>\n<p>www.ambition.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Registration Number: R22104385</p>\n<p>Business Registration Number: 200611680D. Licence Number: 10C5117</p>",
